# üìù Commit Message Template
# 
# Format: <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# <type>: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore
# <scope>: backend, frontend, model, data, config, docs
# <subject>: Brief description (50 chars max)
#
# Example: feat(backend): add real-time detection API
#          fix(frontend): resolve bounding box positioning
#          docs(readme): update installation instructions
#
# ==========================================
# Types:
# feat:     New feature
# fix:      Bug fix
# docs:     Documentation changes
# style:    Formatting, missing semicolons, etc
# refactor: Code restructuring (no functional changes)
# test:     Adding/updating tests
# chore:    Maintenance tasks, deps updates
# perf:     Performance improvements
# build:    Build system or dependency changes
# ci:       CI/CD changes
#
# Scopes:
# backend:  FastAPI, detector, API endpoints
# frontend: React components, UI, styling
# model:    YOLO model, training, evaluation
# data:     Dataset processing, preprocessing
# config:   Configuration files, environment
# docs:     Documentation, README files
# scripts:  Shell scripts, automation
# test:     Test files and test utilities
# ==========================================
#
# Body (optional): Explain what and why, not how
# 
# Footer (optional): 
# - Breaking changes: BREAKING CHANGE: <description>
# - Issue references: Fixes #123, Closes #456
# - Co-authors: Co-authored-by: Name <email>
#
# ==========================================
# Good examples:
# 
# feat(backend): add WebSocket support for real-time detection
# 
# Implements real-time detection streaming using WebSocket
# connections. Clients can now receive detection results
# as they happen without polling the API.
# 
# Fixes #42
#
# ==========================================
# 
# fix(frontend): resolve bounding box coordinate scaling
# 
# Detection boxes were not properly scaled to match video
# dimensions. Fixed coordinate transformation to ensure
# accurate box positioning on all screen sizes.
# 
# BREAKING CHANGE: Detection response format changed
# from xywh to xyxy coordinates
#
# ==========================================
